  "title": "Project Administrator (Construction)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Project Admin Executive </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Project Admin Executive</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Islandwide (Depends on project/ site location)</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $4,300 + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage project documentation and ensure timely submissions</li>\n  <li>Serve as the point of contact for internal teams, external partners, and adjacent community stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Assist Project Manager with schedules, reports, and meetings</li>\n  <li>Raise and follow up on purchase requests with operations team</li>\n  <li>Prepare monthly worker reports and support staff welfare matters</li>\n  <li>Handle inquiries from the public and support liaison activities with relevant regulatory and governing bodies.</li>\n  <li>Maintain document tracking, filing, and overall project organization</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum a Diploma in Business Administration or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in construction administration or site-based roles</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint)</li>\n  <li>Able to work well under pressure and manage multiple tasks</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
